<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

	<ThingDef ParentName="CGF1_MWP_ATLauncher_Disposable_T1">
		<defName>CGF1_MWP_M72_LAW_</defName>
		<label>M72 LAW</label>
		<description>Caliber: 66mm LAW. 1-round tube. Single Use.
		
A portable one-shot unguided anti-tank weapon. Produced beginning in 1963, the LAW was an effective replacement for both the rifle grenades and bazookas used in the anti-tank role up until that point. The M72 is extremely cost effective to produce and very portable, making it a popular platform even in the present.\nThis is the initial production M72 variant, in its most basic form.</description>
